class  FdoIGetLongTransactions
 The FdoIGetLongTransactions interface defines the GetLongTransactions command. It allows a user to retrieve long transaction information for all or a specific long transaction. The command returns a FdoILongTransactionReader object enumerating the identified long transactions. More...
